Nollywood veteran actor Dan Nkoloagu is dead. His death was announced by his son. His son, Dan Nkoloagu Jnr, announced his death on his Facebook page. He said his dad died on January 22. “IT WAS A BLACK FRIDAY FOR US YESTERDAY as my Dad left us without saying goodbye,” he wrote. Nkoloagu, who died at 83, was popular for playing the role of a native doctor in many Igbo movies.